<ABS>  Investigative Report of Surplus Rural Labor </ABS>
<DATE1>   16 February 1994 </DATE1>
<F P=100></F>
<F P=101>   Investigative Report on China's Surplus Rural Labor </F>
<H3> <TI>   Part I </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Part I </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94CM0219A Beijing ZHONGGUO QINGNIAN BAO in Chinese 16 Feb 94 
pp 1, 2 </F>

