<F P=101>   Investigative Report on China's Surplus Rural Labor </F>
<H3> <TI>   Part IV </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Part IV </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94CM0221A Beijing ZHONGGUO QINGNIAN BAO in Chinese 21 Feb 94 
p 3 </F>

